===Noun===
'''crocus''' (''plural'' [[crocuses]] or [[croci]])
# a [[perennial]] flowering [[plant]] (of the ''[[Iridaceae]]'' [[family]]). [[Saffron]] is obtained from the [[stamen]]s of ''[[Crocus sativus]]''.
# some similar flowering plants, such as the [[autumn crocus]] and [[prairie crocus]]

